<paragraph id="IFRS17_B95" base="F55667495"><paranum>B95</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="B95"/></prolog><body><bodydiv base="IFRS2020-3">     <p id="IFRS17_P0829">Unless the premium allocation approach for the <xref base="F55667010" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0551">liability for remaining coverage<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0228"/></ph></xref> in <xref id="IFRS17_X0662" base="F59236446" href="IFRS17_55.dita#IFRS17_55">paragraphs 55&#x2013;59</xref> and <xref href="IFRS17_g69-70.dita">69&#x2013;70A</xref> applies, on initial recognition the <xref base="F55666917" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0519">contractual service margin<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0052"/></ph></xref> is calculated applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0663" base="F59236447" href="IFRS17_g38-39.dita#IFRS17_g38-39/IFRS17_g38-39_TI">paragraph 38</xref> for acquired <xref base="F55666957" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0532">insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0186"/></ph></xref> issued and <xref id="IFRS17_X0664" base="F59236448" href="IFRS17_65.dita#IFRS17_65">paragraph 65</xref> for acquired <xref base="F55667022" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0554">reinsurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0323"/></ph></xref> held using the consideration received or paid for the contracts as a proxy for the premiums received or paid at the date of initial recognition.</p></bodydiv></body></paragraph>